dc_description_s: This data represents roads for Sheboygan County, Wisconsin in 2019. [Road segments representing centerlines of all roadways or carriageways in Sheboygan County. Typically, this information is compiled from orthoimagery or other aerial photography sources. This representation of the road centerlines support address geocoding and mapping. It also serves as a source for public works and other agencies that are responsible for the active management of the road network.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements.For access to the most recent data for this county, please visit: http://data-shebco.opendata.arcgis.com/
